<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en" lang="en"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      i18n:domain="plone">

<tal:comment tal:replace="nothing">
This template based on version from Plone 2.5.2-1

CNX note: pretty much entirely replaced with CNX footer content
          added tal, metal, i18n namespaces for validation purposes

i18nday: jccooper; mostly entirely ours, so now in rhaptos domain
</tal:comment>

<body>
<div id="portal-footer" metal:define-macro="portal_footer" i18n:domain="rhaptos">

    <a id="riceLogo" href="http://www.rice.edu/"><img tal:replace="structure here/ricelogo.gif" /></a>
    <a id="ccLogo" href="http://creativecommons.org">
      <img title="Creative Commons" 
	   alt="Creative Commons"
	   width="80" 
	   height="20" 
	   border="0" 
	   tal:replace="structure here/cc-logo.gif"
           i18n:attributes="title text_creativecommons; alt text_creativecommons" />
    </a>
    <span id="ploneLogo" i18n:domain="plone">
      <a href="http://plone.org">
        <img src=""
            height="15"
            width="80"
            border="0"
            alt="Powered by Plone"
            title="This site was built using the Plone Content Management System. Click for more information."
            tal:attributes="src string:$portal_url/plone_powered.gif;
                            height here/plone_powered.gif/height;
                            width here/plone_powered.gif/width"
            i18n:attributes="alt; title" />
      </a>
    </span>

    <p id="sponsorBlurb" i18n:translate="text_footer_sponsorblurb">
      OpenStax CNX<span i18n:name="registered-tm-symbol"><sup i18n:translate="text_footer_rtmsymbol">&#174;</sup></span> is 
      <span i18n:name="supportedlink">
        <a href="/aboutus/people/sponsors" i18n:translate="link_footer_sponsors">supported</a>
      </span>
      by the <span i18n:name="hewlettfoundation">
        <a href="http://www.hewlett.org/" i18n:translate="link_footer_hewlettfoundation">
         William and Flora Hewlett Foundation</a>, the Maxfield Foundation, and the
         <a href="http://cnxconsortium.org/">OpenStax CNX Consortium</a>.
      </span>
    </p>
    <p i18n:translate="text_footer_tmblurb">
      OpenStax CNX<span i18n:name="registered-tm-symbol"><sup i18n:translate="text_footer_rtmsymbol">&#174;</sup></span> is a registered 
      trademark of Rice University.
    </p>
    <p i18n:translate="text_footer_followus_blurb">Follow us on our <a href="http://blog.cnx.org">blog</a>,
      on
      <a href="http://www.facebook.com/cnx.org"><img src="facebook16x16.ico" alt="facebook icon" style="vertical-align: bottom;" tal:attributes="src string:$portal_url/facebook16x16.ico" /></a>
      <a href="http://www.facebook.com/cnx.org">Facebook</a> on
      <a href="http://twitter.com/cnxorg"><img alt="twitter icon" src="twitter16x16.ico" style="vertical-align: bottom;" tal:attributes="src string:$portal_url/twitter16x16.ico" /></a>
      <a href="http://twitter.com/cnxorg">Twitter</a>, or on 
      <a href="https://plus.google.com/u/0/113721978538758695150?prsrc=3"><img src="https://ssl.gstatic.com/images/icons/gplus-16.png" width="16" height="16" style="border: 0;vertical-align: bottom;"/></a>
      <a href="https://plus.google.com/u/0/113721978538758695150?prsrc=3">Google+</a>    </p>
    <p>
    Use OpenStax CNX <a href="http://cnx.org/android/splash.html">Android App</a>, see our <a href="http://mobile.cnx.org/">mobile site</a>, and find us on <a href="http://itunes.apple.com/us/institution/connexions/id375198208">iTunes U.</a>
    </p>
    <p>For developers: see our <a href="http://devblog.cnx.org/">developer blog</a> and <a href="http://rhaptos.org/">developer site</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="sitelicense" i18n:translate="link_footer_sitelicense" tal:attributes="href string:$portal_url/sitelicense">Site User Agreement</a>
    </p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
